node.text:
Tired of eating homecooked food during the @circuitbreaker.sg ? Well you can always go for roast pork belly/char siew rice from @roastparadise at Old Airport Road Food Centre. That’s what we have for lunch today (14/5). What a great and excellent lunch!😋😋
.
